<div id="sideways">
	<div class="scene" id="hero">

	<h1>Your Personalized Cost of Living Calculator</h1>
	  <div class="half-width pull-left">
	  	<h3>
	  		Are you the same as your neighbor?
	  	</h3>
	  	<div class="lead">
	  		The Bureau of Labor Statistics thinks so. They treat everyone the same.
	  	</div>
	  	<div class="lead">
	  		At Cost of Living Card we believe that your cost of living is personal.
	  	</div>
	  </div>
	  <div class="pull-right half-width push-up">
	  	<%= image_tag 'blsseesyou.jpg' %>
	  	<div class="text-center">
	  		<%= link_to "Get Started (Its Free!)", "#problem", class:'btn btn-large btn-primary next' %>
	  	</div>
	  </div>
	</div>

	<div class="scene" id="problem">
		<h3>Spending Breakdown</h3>
		<div class="muted">Standard Urban Consumer</div>
		<ul>
			<li>
				Apparel
			</li>
			<li>
				Food & Beverage
			</li>
			<li>
				Technology
			</li>
			<li>
				Medical
			</li>
			<li>
				Education
			</li>			
			<li>
				Personal Care
			</li>
			<li>
				Recreation
			</li>
			<li>
				Transport
			</li>
			<li>
				Housing
			</li>
		</ul>
	</div>

	<div class="scene" id="problem">

	<h1>It doesn't add up.</h1>
	<p>When they say that inflation is only 1.5%. <br> <br>
		In reality inflation is different for everyone, and for most it is  between <strong>3-5%</strong>.</p> 

	<h1>Your one of Millions</h1>
		<p>Since 2007 US households have increased their savings <strong>300%.</strong><br><br>
			Over the same time, interest rates fell to <strong>record lows.</strong>
		</p>


	<h1>Pay Anywhere, Save Everywhere</h1>
	<p>We provide a <strong>universal payment network</strong>,<br><br> and we aggregate living costs across the US <strong>your savings</strong> travel with you.</p>


	</div>

	<div class="scene" id="join">

		<h2>Join</h2>
	<%= form_for @email_subscription do |f| %>
	  <% if @email_subscription.errors.any? %>
	    <div id="error_explanation">
	      <h2><%= pluralize(@email_subscription.errors.count, "error") %> prohibited this email_subscription from being saved:</h2>

	      <ul>
	      <% @email_subscription.errors.full_messages.each do |msg| %>
	        <li><%= msg %></li>
	      <% end %>
	      </ul>
	    </div>
	  <% end %>

	  <%= f.label :email %></br>
		<%= f.text_field :email %><br>
		<%= f.submit "Signup" %>
	<% end %>
	</div>
</div>